Invocation Name: eco warrior
des: Find out a wide range of helpful tips and trivia to help you get to a better carbon footprint for you and your family. You'll get interesting tips regarding how to save energy (and money!) on appliances, your home, during travelling, at work, out and about, etc. Your contribution makes a difference!
